00:44:16,404 --> 00:44:18,823
It's, you know, the bloke
who lives in the Ritz all the time.

708
00:44:18,948 --> 00:44:20,700
So, we went there.

709
00:44:20,825 --> 00:44:25,037
All right now, this is
