722
00:45:02,200 --> 00:45:05,494
Open bar. Anybody who come here,
you get free drinks.

723
00:45:05,620 --> 00:45:10,041
He runs an open tab.
That's him. He's very generous.

724
00:45:10,541 --> 00:45:13,711
Guys that are down,
he brings them up, you know?

725
00:45:13,836 --> 00:45:15,129
