898
00:55:52,140 --> 00:55:54,601
because you'd walk into the store
and go,

899
00:55:54,726 --> 00:55:57,729
"I'll have a bottle of shampoo,
packet of razorblades,

900
00:55:57,855 --> 00:55:59,857
50 Valium and a Mars bar."

